{"tid":925241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱刺的歌 ！忽爾靜了！ 倫敦！ 一聲慘叫~~~~~~","createTime":"2018-12-02T15:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T17:15:07.000Z","uid":38841,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4918dfcdf390f8efad1cdb11a9c2ecb22a5d5345","tid":925241,"uid":38841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T15:56:24.000Z","msg":"熱刺的歌　忽爾靜了 <br />\n倫敦　一聲慘叫 <br />\n歐冠位也沒了　四弟你被忘掉 <br />\n爭冠 預了失分惡兆 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又無三分　失控地笑　場邊　終於哭了 <br />\n失季軍也定了　你第四但心照 <br />\n那托定咸熱刺　不妙了 <br />\n<br />\n*當歐冠聯結束　車仔派對舞曲 <br />\n阿記曾像這樣　爭標大概相似 <br />\n總有十年　落入這種困局 <br />\n<br />\n熱刺今天　聲勢大了 <br />\n倫敦　一哥想要 <br />\n成功的季度流走了　列阿利曾經這樣了* <br />\n<br />\n鹿徑風光　一剎沒了 <br />\n銅獎　手中丟了 <br />\n輸過炒過敗過　那熱刺被速秒 <br />\n猛將下場就要　走掉了 <br />\n<br />\nRepeat * <br />\n<br />\n是　所有熱迷會走掉　一發現已經淪落了"},{"pid":"9d1cb69ec7e8cfcfce804caeb8babde436f29732","tid":925241,"uid":77355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T15:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ho ball"},{"pid":"b12f8dcfc4777755ec191fd34a140c2e3eff5aeb","tid":925241,"uid":141725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:02:27.000Z","msg":"此貼必火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fce1f573e0581ec79963892bf5b34c0959ff0c","tid":925241,"uid":38841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb83b00b8bac0da146d8775f989cc84f74f9d40","tid":925241,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T16:07:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/knW5qfxHa_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FknW5qfxHa_k&d=6KqC%2BRlu7fUPzwnyrQUOUf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a8f60f0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/knW5qfxHa_k</a>"},{"pid":"98638ce902d